# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Edu Bot Environment Configuration
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file to .env:  cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in your actual values
# 3. NEVER commit .env to version control
# 4. Keep your tokens secret!
#
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── REQUIRED ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Telegram Bot Token from @BotFather
# Get it from: https://t.me/BotFather
# Format: 1234567890:ABCdefGHIjklMNOpqrsTUVwxyz
TELEGRAM_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token_here

# ─── OPTIONAL (but recommended) ───────────────────────────────

# Groq AI API Key for chat features
# Get it from: https://console.groq.com/keys
# Format: gsk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# Note: Bot works without this, but AI chat will be disabled
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Admin Telegram User ID for management commands
# Get your ID from: @userinfobot on Telegram
# Format: 123456789 (numbers only)
# Note: Only this user can access /bookings, /stats, /reload
ADMIN_ID=your_telegram_user_id_here

# ─── OPTIONAL (advanced) ──────────────────────────────────────

# Custom knowledge base file path
# Default: knowledge.txt in the same directory
# You can specify absolute or relative path
KNOWLEDGE_FILE=knowledge.txt

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SECURITY NOTES:
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. File Permissions:
#    chmod 600 .env
#    (Only owner can read/write)
#
# 2. Never commit .env:
#    Add to .gitignore:
#    echo ".env" >> .gitignore
#
# 3. Rotate tokens regularly:
#    - Use @BotFather to revoke old tokens
#    - Generate new ones if compromised
#
# 4. Backup safely:
#    - If backing up, ensure backups are encrypted
#    - Never store in public repositories
#
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
